headline: Lockheed Martin Tumbles On Earnings. Here's Why.
summary: Lockheed Martin posts major earnings miss. Northrop Grumman lifts outlook. RTX cut its earnings forecast.

headline: Lockheed Martin (LMT) Q2 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: Lockheed (LMT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +12.33% and -2.21%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
